      "content": "it's not just a \"setback\" though. it's a total erasure. my name is basically radioactive now in this industry. i can't \"rebuild\" when the people i trust most are looking at me like i've committed a crime. the debt is basically a life sentence. every time i close my eyes i just see the spreadsheets and the look on my wife's face. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to not feel this crushing weight for once.",
